      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Serverless is hiring temp staff by the task — perfect for greeting webhooks and taking orders, while dedicated kitchen staff (containers) cook the long agent meals."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Key takeaways"
